Log In Page:
As a developer I would like to create a log-in page which has the following functionality:
-Asks user for username
-Asks user for password
-User should be given a hint incase they forget their password

As a developer I would like to have the following functionalities in the log-in page:
-Lock-out if too many failed atempts were made
-Provide security question for password recovery/change

As a developer I would like the app to have the following:
-A data-base of all transactions
-Ability for users to keep track of their loans and debts

